data.meta_description: WHNS, branded Fox Carolina, is a television station licensed to Greenville, South Carolina, United States, serving as the Fox affiliate for Upstate South Carolina and Western North Carolina. Owned by Gray Television, the station maintains studios on Interstate Court in Greenville, and its transmitter is located atop Slick Rock Mountain in Transylvania County, North Carolina.
